research.thaumicmyths_root.text0=The ever-occurring tasks of dealing with the undead and their companions had me question whether or not I am the only being capable of utilizing magic to my advantage. After some thought I came to the conclusion that, given the size of this world, I would likely not be or have been the only one to discover thaumaturgy and its secrets. The thought of a magician more advanced frightens me but has also sparked my curiosity.<BR>I should dedicate this chapter to any findings related to other magicians I might discover.